	<h1 class="title">杨浩涌辞任58赶集联席CEO，他能带独立出来的瓜子走多远？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-25 19:56:38 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18072/medium/18072.jpg?1448451764" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


